      <section class="visual">
        <div class="visual__image">
        </div>
        <div class="container-lg px-3 px-sm-4 px-xl-5">
          <div class="visual__text-banner">
            <h1 class="visual__title">Still in contract?
            </h1>
            <p class="visual__text">Complete our short questionnaire and we'll make sure you hear about our best offers when your current broadband contract expires.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="container-outer">
    <div class="container-lg px-3 px-sm-4 px-xl-5">
      <div class="center-content">
        <form id="telcoSurvey" class="form" name="telcoSurvey" action="" method="post">
          <input type="hidden" name ="billingAccountId" value = "">
          <input type="hidden" name ="subscriberKey" value = "">
          <input type="hidden" name ="externalAccountId" value = "">
          <input type="hidden" name ="emailName" value = "">
            <div class="form__group d-block mb-5">
              <fieldset>
              <legend class="form__legend">When does your broadband contract expire? </legend>
              <p class="form__text">If you aren't sure on the exact date, you can always check your previous bills, online account or contact your supplier directly - doing this now could save you money in the long run.</p>
              <div class="form__input-container">
                <p class="mb-0">
                  <span class="d-block text-bold">Expiry date</span>
                  <span class="d-block">E.g 11/08/2021</span>
                </p>
                <div class="form__inputs-wrapper">
                  <input type="number" id="dateOfExpDay" class="form__input-date" name="dateOfExpDay" min="1" max="31" placeholder="DD" required aria-label="Day of date of contract expiry">
                  <input type="number" id="dateOfExpMonth" class="form__input-date" name="dateOfExpMonth" min="1" max="12" placeholder="MM" required aria-label="Month of date of contract expiry">
                  <input type="number" id="dateOfExpYear" class="form__input-date" name="dateOfExpYear" min="0" max="0" placeholder="YYYY" required aria-label="Year of date of contract expiry">
                </div>
                <p class="form__error-message" aria-live="assertive">Required</p>
              </div>
            </fieldset>
            </div>
            <div class="form__group mb-5">
              <fieldset>
              <legend class="form__legend">Who is your broadband provider?</legend>
              <div class="form__input-container">
                <div class="form__inputs-wrapper">
                  <ul class="form__tiles">
                    <li class="form__tiles__item">
                      <label class="form__tiles_label">
                        <input type="radio" id="virginMedia" class="form__tiles__input" name="broadbandProvider" value="Virgin Media" required>
                        <span data-test="virginMedia" class="form__tiles__radio">Virgin Media</span>
                      </label>
                    </li>
                    <li class="form__tiles__item">
                      <label class="form__tiles_label">
                        <input type="radio" id="sky" class="form__tiles__input" name="broadbandProvider" value="Sky" required>
                        <span data-test="sky" class="form__tiles__radio">Sky</span>
                      </label>
                    </li>
                    <li class="form__tiles__item">
                      <label class="form__tiles_label">
                        <input type="radio" id="BT" class="form__tiles__input" name="broadbandProvider" value="BT" required>
                        <span data-test="BT" class="form__tiles__radio">BT</span>
                      </label>
                    </li>
                    <li class="form__tiles__item">
                      <label class="form__tiles_label">
                        <input type="radio" id="plusnet" class="form__tiles__input" name="broadbandProvider" value="Plusnet" required>
                        <span data-test="plusnet" class="form__tiles__radio">Plusnet</span>
                      </label>
                    </li>
                    <li class="form__tiles__item">
                      <label class="form__tiles_label">
                        <input type="radio" id="vodafone" class="form__tiles__input" name="broadbandProvider" value="Vodafone" required>
                        <span data-test="vodafone" class="form__tiles__radio">Vodafone</span>
                      </label>
                    </li>
                    <li class="form__tiles__item">
                      <label class="form__tiles_label">
                        <input type="radio" id="ee" class="form__tiles__input" name="broadbandProvider" value="EE" required>
                        <span data-test="ee" class="form__tiles__radio">EE</span>
                      </label>
                    </li>
                    <li class="form__tiles__item">
                      <label class="form__tiles_label">
                        <input type="radio" id="talkTalk" class="form__tiles__input" name="broadbandProvider" value="TalkTalk" required>
                        <span data-test="talkTalk" class="form__tiles__radio">TalkTalk</span>
                      </label>
                    </li>
                    <li class="form__tiles__item">
                      <label class="form__tiles_label">
                        <input type="radio" id="otherProvider" class="form__tiles__input" name="broadbandProvider" value="other" required>
                        <span data-test="other" class="form__tiles__radio">Other</span>
                      </label>
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                <div id="broadbandProviderOtherBox" class="mt-3">
                  <label for="broadbandProviderOther" class="text-bold">Providers name</label>
                  <div class="form__inputs-wrapper">
                  <input type="text" id="broadbandProviderOther" class="form__input-secondary" name="broadbandProviderOther" maxlength="50">
                  </div>
                </div>
                <p class="form__error-message" aria-live="assertive">Required</p>
              </div>
            </fieldset>
            </div>
            <div class="form__group mb-5">
              <fieldset>
              <legend class="form__legend">How fast is your broadband package?</legend>
              <div class="form__input-container">
                <label for="existingBroadbandSpeed" class="text-bold">Broadband speeds (Optional)</label>
                <span class="d-block">Typically the average upload speed</span>
                <div class="form__inputs-wrapper">
                  <select id="existingBroadbandSpeed" class="form__input-select" name="existingBroadbandSpeed">
                    <option value="" selected>Select...</option>
                    <option value="0-30">0 - 30 Mbps</option>
                    <option value="31-60">31 - 60 Mbps</option>
                    <option value="61-100">61 - 100 Mbps</option>
                    <option value="101-300">101 - 300 Mbps</option>
                    <option value="301-500">301 - 500 Mbps</option>
                    <option value="500+">500+ Mbps</option>
                  </select>
                </div>
                <p class="form__error-message" aria-live="assertive">Required</p>
              </div>
            </fieldset>
            </div>
            <div class="form__group mb-5">
              <fieldset>
              <legend class="form__legend">How much do you pay per month for broadband?</legend>
              <div class="form__input-container">
                <label for="monthlyCost" class="text-bold">Monthly cost (Optional)</label>
                <div class="form__inputs-wrapper">
                  <input type="text" id="monthlyCost" class="form__input-text" name="monthlyCost" value="�" maxlength="8" placeholder="�">
                </div>
                <p class="form__error-message" aria-live="assertive">Required</p>
              </div>
            </fieldset>
            </div>
            <div class="form__group mb-4">
              <fieldset>
              <legend class="form__legend">Are there any additional products included in your plan?</legend>
              <div class="form__input-container">
                <p class="mb-0">
                  <span class="d-block text-bold">Additional products (Optional)</span>
                </p>
                <div class="form__inputs-wrapper">
                  <ul class="form__checkboxes">
                    <li class="form__checkboxes__item">
                      <label class="form__checkboxes__label">Call package
                        <input type="checkbox" id="callPackage" class="form__checkboxes__input" name="additionalProducts" value="callPackage">
                        <span class="form__checkboxes__checkmark"></span>
                      </label>
                    </li>
                    <li class="form__checkboxes__item">
                      <label class="form__checkboxes__label">TV package
                        <input type="checkbox" id="tvPackage" class="form__checkboxes__input" name="additionalProducts" value="tvPackage">
                        <span class="form__checkboxes__checkmark"></span>
                      </label>
                    </li>
                    <li class="form__checkboxes__item">
                      <label class="form__checkboxes__label">Mobile
                        <input type="checkbox" id="mobile" class="form__checkboxes__input" name="additionalProducts" value="mobile">
                        <span class="form__checkboxes__checkmark"></span>
                      </label>
                    </li>
                    <li class="form__checkboxes__item">
                      <label class="form__checkboxes__label">Streaming services
                        <input type="checkbox" id="streamingServices" class="form__checkboxes__input" name="additionalProducts" value="streamingServices">
                        <span class="form__checkboxes__checkmark"></span>
                      </label>
                    </li>
                    <li class="form__checkboxes__item">
                      <label class="form__checkboxes__label">Other
                        <input type="checkbox" id="otherProducts" class="form__checkboxes__input" name="additionalProducts" value="otherProducts">
                        <span class="form__checkboxes__checkmark"></span>
                      </label>
                    </li>
                  </ul>
              </div>
              <div id="additionalProductsOtherBox" class="mt-3">
                <label for="additionalProductsOther" class="text-bold">Other products</label>
                <div class="form__inputs-wrapper">
                <input type="text" id="additionalProductsOther" class="form__input-secondary" name="additionalProductsOther" maxlength="100">
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="form__error-message" aria-live="assertive">Required</p>
            </div>
            </fieldset>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="form__buttons-bar">
                <button type="button" id="prevBtn" class="form__button form__button--secondary">Back</button>
                <button type="button" id="nextBtn" class="form__button form__button--primary">Next Step</button>
              </div>
            </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
    
</main>
<!-- Footer -->
<footer id="footer" class="footer py-4">
  <div class="container-lg px-3 px-sm-4 px-xl-5">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-12">
        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="small m-0">� 2010 - <span id="footerCurrentYear">2020</span> Shell Energy Retail Limited
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
<!-- Optional JavaScript -->
<!-- jQuery first, then Popper.js, then Bootstrap JS -->
<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.4.1.min.js" integrity="sha256-CSXorXvZcTkaix6Yvo6HppcZGetbYMGWSFlBw8HfCJo=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.9.2/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-IQsoLXl5PILFhosVNubq5LC7Qb9DXgDA9i+tQ8Zj3iwWAwPtgFTxbJ8NT4GN1R8p" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-lpyLfhYuitXl2zRZ5Bn2fqnhNAKOAaM/0Kr9laMspuaMiZfGmfwRNFh8HlMy49eQ" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

<!-- Setting up the current year in the footer-->
<script>
  const now = new Date();
  const currentYear = now.getFullYear();
  document.getElementById("footerCurrentYear").innerHTML = currentYear;
</script>

</body>
</html>

    <main class="main">
     
    
    
      <section class="visual">
        <div class="visual__image">
        </div>
        <div class="container-lg px-3 px-sm-4 px-xl-5">
          <div class="visual__text-banner">
            <h1 class="visual__title">Still in contract?
            </h1>
            <p class="visual__text">Complete our short questionnaire and we'll make sure you hear about our best offers when your current broadband contract expires.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="container-outer">
    <div class="container-lg px-3 px-sm-4 px-xl-5">
      <div class="center-content">
        <form id="telcoSurvey" class="form" name="telcoSurvey" action="" method="post">
          <input type="hidden" name ="billingAccountId" value = "">
          <input type="hidden" name ="subscriberKey" value = "">
          <input type="hidden" name ="externalAccountId" value = "">
          <input type="hidden" name ="emailName" value = "">
            <div class="form__group d-block mb-5">
              <fieldset>
              <legend class="form__legend">When does your broadband contract expire? </legend>
              <p class="form__text">If you aren't sure on the exact date, you can always check your previous bills, online account or contact your supplier directly - doing this now could save you money in the long run.</p>
              <div class="form__input-container">
                <p class="mb-0">
                  <span class="d-block text-bold">Expiry date</span>
                  <span class="d-block">E.g 11/08/2021</span>
                </p>
                <div class="form__inputs-wrapper">
                  <input type="number" id="dateOfExpDay" class="form__input-date" name="dateOfExpDay" min="1" max="31" placeholder="DD" required aria-label="Day of date of contract expiry">
                  <input type="number" id="dateOfExpMonth" class="form__input-date" name="dateOfExpMonth" min="1" max="12" placeholder="MM" required aria-label="Month of date of contract expiry">
                  <input type="number" id="dateOfExpYear" class="form__input-date" name="dateOfExpYear" min="0" max="0" placeholder="YYYY" required aria-label="Year of date of contract expiry">
                </div>
                <p class="form__error-message" aria-live="assertive">Required</p>
              </div>
            </fieldset>
            </div>
            <div class="form__group mb-5">
              <fieldset>
              <legend class="form__legend">Who is your broadband provider?</legend>
              <div class="form__input-container">
                <div class="form__inputs-wrapper">
                  <ul class="form__tiles">
                    <li class="form__tiles__item">
                      <label class="form__tiles_label">
                        <input type="radio" id="virginMedia" class="form__tiles__input" name="broadbandProvider" value="Virgin Media" required>
                        <span data-test="virginMedia" class="form__tiles__radio">Virgin Media</span>
                      </label>
                    </li>
                    <li class="form__tiles__item">
                      <label class="form__tiles_label">
                        <input type="radio" id="sky" class="form__tiles__input" name="broadbandProvider" value="Sky" required>
                        <span data-test="sky" class="form__tiles__radio">Sky</span>
                      </label>
                    </li>
                    <li class="form__tiles__item">
                      <label class="form__tiles_label">
                        <input type="radio" id="BT" class="form__tiles__input" name="broadbandProvider" value="BT" required>
                        <span data-test="BT" class="form__tiles__radio">BT</span>
                      </label>
                    </li>
                    <li class="form__tiles__item">
                      <label class="form__tiles_label">
                        <input type="radio" id="plusnet" class="form__tiles__input" name="broadbandProvider" value="Plusnet" required>
                        <span data-test="plusnet" class="form__tiles__radio">Plusnet</span>
                      </label>
                    </li>
                    <li class="form__tiles__item">
                      <label class="form__tiles_label">
                        <input type="radio" id="vodafone" class="form__tiles__input" name="broadbandProvider" value="Vodafone" required>
                        <span data-test="vodafone" class="form__tiles__radio">Vodafone</span>
                      </label>
                    </li>
                    <li class="form__tiles__item">
                      <label class="form__tiles_label">
                        <input type="radio" id="ee" class="form__tiles__input" name="broadbandProvider" value="EE" required>
                        <span data-test="ee" class="form__tiles__radio">EE</span>
                      </label>
                    </li>
                    <li class="form__tiles__item">
                      <label class="form__tiles_label">
                        <input type="radio" id="talkTalk" class="form__tiles__input" name="broadbandProvider" value="TalkTalk" required>
                        <span data-test="talkTalk" class="form__tiles__radio">TalkTalk</span>
                      </label>
                    </li>
                    <li class="form__tiles__item">
                      <label class="form__tiles_label">
                        <input type="radio" id="otherProvider" class="form__tiles__input" name="broadbandProvider" value="other" required>
                        <span data-test="other" class="form__tiles__radio">Other</span>
                      </label>
                    </li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                <div id="broadbandProviderOtherBox" class="mt-3">
                  <label for="broadbandProviderOther" class="text-bold">Providers name</label>
                  <div class="form__inputs-wrapper">
                  <input type="text" id="broadbandProviderOther" class="form__input-secondary" name="broadbandProviderOther" maxlength="50">
                  </div>
                </div>
                <p class="form__error-message" aria-live="assertive">Required</p>
              </div>
            </fieldset>
            </div>
            <div class="form__group mb-5">
              <fieldset>
              <legend class="form__legend">How fast is your broadband package?</legend>
              <div class="form__input-container">
                <label for="existingBroadbandSpeed" class="text-bold">Broadband speeds (Optional)</label>
                <span class="d-block">Typically the average upload speed</span>
                <div class="form__inputs-wrapper">
                  <select id="existingBroadbandSpeed" class="form__input-select" name="existingBroadbandSpeed">
                    <option value="" selected>Select...</option>
                    <option value="0-30">0 - 30 Mbps</option>
                    <option value="31-60">31 - 60 Mbps</option>
                    <option value="61-100">61 - 100 Mbps</option>
                    <option value="101-300">101 - 300 Mbps</option>
                    <option value="301-500">301 - 500 Mbps</option>
                    <option value="500+">500+ Mbps</option>
                  </select>
                </div>
                <p class="form__error-message" aria-live="assertive">Required</p>
              </div>
            </fieldset>
            </div>
            <div class="form__group mb-5">
              <fieldset>
              <legend class="form__legend">How much do you pay per month for broadband?</legend>
              <div class="form__input-container">
                <label for="monthlyCost" class="text-bold">Monthly cost (Optional)</label>
                <div class="form__inputs-wrapper">
                  <input type="text" id="monthlyCost" class="form__input-text" name="monthlyCost" value="�" maxlength="8" placeholder="�">
                </div>
                <p class="form__error-message" aria-live="assertive">Required</p>
              </div>
            </fieldset>
            </div>
            <div class="form__group mb-4">
              <fieldset>
              <legend class="form__legend">Are there any additional products included in your plan?</legend>
              <div class="form__input-container">
                <p class="mb-0">
                  <span class="d-block text-bold">Additional products (Optional)</span>
                </p>
                <div class="form__inputs-wrapper">
                  <ul class="form__checkboxes">
                    <li class="form__checkboxes__item">
                      <label class="form__checkboxes__label">Call package
                        <input type="checkbox" id="callPackage" class="form__checkboxes__input" name="additionalProducts" value="callPackage">
                        <span class="form__checkboxes__checkmark"></span>
                      </label>
                    </li>
                    <li class="form__checkboxes__item">
                      <label class="form__checkboxes__label">TV package
                        <input type="checkbox" id="tvPackage" class="form__checkboxes__input" name="additionalProducts" value="tvPackage">
                        <span class="form__checkboxes__checkmark"></span>
                      </label>
                    </li>
                    <li class="form__checkboxes__item">
                      <label class="form__checkboxes__label">Mobile
                        <input type="checkbox" id="mobile" class="form__checkboxes__input" name="additionalProducts" value="mobile">
                        <span class="form__checkboxes__checkmark"></span>
                      </label>
                    </li>
                    <li class="form__checkboxes__item">
                      <label class="form__checkboxes__label">Streaming services
                        <input type="checkbox" id="streamingServices" class="form__checkboxes__input" name="additionalProducts" value="streamingServices">
                        <span class="form__checkboxes__checkmark"></span>
                      </label>
                    </li>
                    <li class="form__checkboxes__item">
                      <label class="form__checkboxes__label">Other
                        <input type="checkbox" id="otherProducts" class="form__checkboxes__input" name="additionalProducts" value="otherProducts">
                        <span class="form__checkboxes__checkmark"></span>
                      </label>
                    </li>
                  </ul>
              </div>
              <div id="additionalProductsOtherBox" class="mt-3">
                <label for="additionalProductsOther" class="text-bold">Other products</label>
                <div class="form__inputs-wrapper">
                <input type="text" id="additionalProductsOther" class="form__input-secondary" name="additionalProductsOther" maxlength="100">
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="form__error-message" aria-live="assertive">Required</p>
            </div>
            </fieldset>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="form__buttons-bar">
                <button type="button" id="prevBtn" class="form__button form__button--secondary">Back</button>
                <button type="button" id="nextBtn" class="form__button form__button--primary">Next Step</button>
              </div>
            </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
    
</main>
<!-- Footer -->
<footer id="footer" class="footer py-4">
  <div class="container-lg px-3 px-sm-4 px-xl-5">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-12">
        <div class="text-center">
          <p class="small m-0">� 2010 - <span id="footerCurrentYear">2020</span> Shell Energy Retail Limited
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
<!-- Optional JavaScript -->
<!-- jQuery first, then Popper.js, then Bootstrap JS -->
<script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.4.1.min.js" integrity="sha256-CSXorXvZcTkaix6Yvo6HppcZGetbYMGWSFlBw8HfCJo=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@popperjs/core@2.9.2/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-IQsoLXl5PILFhosVNubq5LC7Qb9DXgDA9i+tQ8Zj3iwWAwPtgFTxbJ8NT4GN1R8p" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-lpyLfhYuitXl2zRZ5Bn2fqnhNAKOAaM/0Kr9laMspuaMiZfGmfwRNFh8HlMy49eQ" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>

<!-- Setting up the current year in the footer-->
<script>
  const now = new Date();
  const currentYear = now.getFullYear();
  document.getElementById("footerCurrentYear").innerHTML = currentYear;
</script>

</body>
